---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Free Guide: Build Your AI-Native Website in an Afternoon - Ross Starkey"
  description="Step-by-step guide to building a fast, modern website with AI. No coding experience required. Get the complete guide delivered to your inbox."
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight">
        Build Your AI-Native Website<br/>in an Afternoon
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
        A complete step-by-step guide to creating a fast, modern website without writing a single line of code. Built for AI to manage, designed to last.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- What You'll Get Section -->
    <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-8 mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6">What's Inside the Guide</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-4">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-teal-400 mt-1 shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
          </span>
          <span class="text-gray-300">Complete installation guide for Mac and Windows (no tech knowledge required)</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-teal-400 mt-1 shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
          </span>
          <span class="text-gray-300">The exact stack I used (Astro + Tailwind + Vercel + Claude Code)</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-teal-400 mt-1 shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
          </span>
          <span class="text-gray-300">Step-by-step setup instructions written for complete beginners</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-teal-400 mt-1 shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
          </span>
          <span class="text-gray-300">How to use AI to write all the code for you (just describe what you want)</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-teal-400 mt-1 shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
          </span>
          <span class="text-gray-300">Free hosting setup that deploys changes in 30 seconds</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-teal-400 mt-1 shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
          </span>
          <span class="text-gray-300">Common issues and how to fix them (troubleshooting section included)</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
          <span class="text-teal-400 mt-1 shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
          </span>
          <span class="text-gray-300">The foundation for eventually connecting AI agents to manage your site</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Form Section -->
    <div class="bg-gray-900/50 border border-teal-500/30 rounded-xl p-8 md:p-12 text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Get the Complete Guide</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Enter your email below and I'll send you the full step-by-step guide (PDF) instantly. No spam, no fluff. Just the exact process I used.
      </p>

      <!-- TinyEmail Form -->
      <div class="max-w-md mx-auto">
        <div><script src="https://app.tinyemail.com/static/js/TinyFormRenderer.js" data-ia1="b0b07f82-f37d-43e6-8e45-2ca461703ecf" data-if2="858430d9-7052-4045-a981-b9b5e2a99e32"></script></div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-6">
        I respect your inbox. Unsubscribe anytime.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Social Proof / About Section -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
        I'm Ross Starkey, a 787 pilot who built this website without writing a single line of code. This guide documents exactly how I did it.
      </p>
      <a href="/" class="text-teal-400 hover:text-teal-300 font-medium">
        See the site this guide built â†’
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
